snippet.title: Fire Emblem Engage — Expansion Pass Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Engage with Emblems, battles, maps and more in the #FireEmblem Engage Expansion Pass! Four packs of additional content await, starting when Wave 1 launches on 1/20, alongside the release of Fire Emblem Engage.

Are you ready re-engage with the Wave 1 Emblem characters?

https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/fire-emblem-engage-switch/

#FireEmblem #NintendoSwitch
